"{\"uid\": \"flotrack.org-articles-12743698-what-is-a-repechage-round-at-the-2024-olympics-heres-what-to-know\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Redlands Invitational  Chandler Rotary Invite  Adidas Indoor Nationals  Texas Distance Festival  W&L Outdoor T&F Carnival  Run Rome the Marathon  David Noble Relays  Emory Thrills in the Hills  WashU Distance Carnival  Jim Taylor Duals  Doc Jopson Invitational  2026 FSU Relays  Continental Tour: Maurie Plant Meet  WashU Invite  Monmouth Home Opener  So what is a \\\"repechage round,\\\" you may ask?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_F._Noble\", \"score\": 0.9999895151267415, \"rank\": 6.885312829895756e-06, \"text\": \"David Noble\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_F._Noble\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_F._Noble\"}, {\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monmouth_University\", \"score\": 0.9539577225610575, \"rank\": 0.048240351145006376, \"text\": \"Monmouth\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monmouth_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monmouth_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Athletics Council approved the format change ahead of the 2024 track and field competition at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999989500289358, \"rank\": 1.0499721319899203e-06, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The specifics are pretty simple.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic track and field athletes who do not automatically qualify through the first round of action in the 200m, 400m, 800m, 1,500m, 100mH, 110mH and 400mH will be granted an additional round to secure their spots into the semifinals.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes who automatically qualify through to the semifinals will continue their medal quest, with a potential three rounds of competition.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes who do not qualify initially, however, will have as many as four rounds.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each athlete in those event disciplines will be guaranteed at least two rounds of competition.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"World Athletics President Seb Coe said of the format change, \\\"the repechage rounds will give more exposure to our sport during the peak Olympic period and will be carefully scheduled to ensure that every event on our Olympic program retains its share of the spotlight.\\\"\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999989500289358, \"rank\": 1.0499721319899203e-06, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seb Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"August 5 -- Men's 200m Round 1  August 6 - Men's 200m Repechage Round  August 7 - Men's 200m Semifinal  August 8 - Men's 200m Final  August 4 - Men's 400m Round 1  August 5 - Men's 400m Repechage Round  August 6 - Men's 400m Semifinal  August 7 - Men's 400m Final  August 7 - Men's 800m Round 1  August 8 - Men's 800m Repechage Round  August 9 - Men's 800m Semifinal  August 2 - Men's 1,500m Round 1  August 3 - Men's 1,500m Repechage Round  August 4 - Men's 1,500m Semifinal  August 6 - Men's 1,500m Final  August 4 - Men's 110mH \\u00a0Round 1  August 6 - Men's 110mH Repechage Round  August 7 - Men's 110mH Semifinal  August 8 - Men's 110mH Final  August 5 - Men's 400mH Round 1  August 6 - Men's 400mH Repechage Round  August 7 - Men's 400mH Semifinal  August 9 - Men's 400mH Final  August 4 - Women's 200m Round 1  August 5 - Women's 200m Repechage Round  August 6 - Women's 200m Final  August 5 - Women's 400m Round 1  August 6 - Women's 400m Repechage Round  August 7 - Women's 400m Semifinal  August 9 - Women's 400m Final  August 2 - Women's 800m Round 1  August 3 - Women's 800m Repechage Round  August 4 - Women's 800m Semifinal  August 5 - Women's 800m Final  August 6 - Women's 1,500m Round 1  August 7 - Women's 1,500m Repechage Round  August 8 - Women's 1,500m Semifinal  August 10 - Women's 1,500m Final  August 7 - Women's 100mH Round 1  August 8 - Women's 100mH Repechage Round  August 9 - Women's 100mHSemifinal  August 10 - Women's 100mH Final  August 4 - Women's 400mH Round 1  August 5 - Women's 400mH Repechage Round  August 6 - Women's 400mH Semifinal  August 8 - Women's 400mH Final  The Olympics begin on July 26 and end on August 11.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 3036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The track and field events will begin on Aug. 1.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss all the track and field season action streaming on FloTrack.Check out the FloTrack schedule for more events.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Video footage from each event will be archived and stored in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.152955768381677e-38, \"text\": \"Track & Field\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": []}]}"